Parliament, Thursday, 16 August 2018 – At its meeting that took place on 8 August 2018, the Joint Committee on Ethics and Members’ Interests, took a decision that the deadline for the annual disclosures of Members Financial Interest for 2018 is Wednesday, 10 October 2018. ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES ON BEHALF OF THE CO-CHAIRPERSONS OF THE JOINT COMMITTEE ON ETHICS AND MEMBERS’ INTERESTS, MR AMOS MASONDO AND AUMSEN SINGH. For media enquiries or interviews with the Co-Chairpersons, please contact the committee’s Media Officer: Name: Mava Lukani (Mr)
